Package com.mogreet.mercury

Provides the classes necessary to create a Mercury object (requests) and a Response object.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Mercury The Mercury is an object that allows to execute three types of requests (system, user and transaction) to the Moms API.
Response Response is the super class for all the kind of responses that can be obtained from the Moms API requests.
 

Package com.mogreet.mercury Description
